NACounter
=========
A counter control that mimicks the old style roller counter/tickers.

How to use
----------

1. Copy all of the files into your project (You may want to customise the images to the look and feel of your app)
2. Include `NACounter.h` in the controller you'd like to use this
3. Create a new counter using `initWithFrame` and add to the current view
4. Update the counter with `updateCounter`, `incrementCounter` and `decrementCounter`

